channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] Match 360 (mdm-oc) has changed the description of the plan named essential-edition
item.description:
*before*: This plan provides you with the core capabilities of IBM Match 360, a multi-domain operational and analytical master data management (MDM) service that delivers at scale an integrated and consolidated view of critical enterprise data across data silos, leveraging intelligent and tunable data matching and entity resolution as well as management of other related entities across the enterprise.
*** Advanced governance and quality capabilities, including support for Al assisted profiling and mapping, data quality assessment of inputs and resolved entities, as well as enforcing enterprise data quality and privacy policies for master data is provided by an additional subscription of IBM watsonx.data intelligence Standard plan., *after*: This plan provides you with the core capabilities of IBM Master Data Management, a multi-domain operational and analytical master data management (MDM) service that delivers at scale an integrated and consolidated view of critical enterprise data across data silos, leveraging intelligent and tunable data matching and entity resolution as well as management of other related entities across the enterprise.
*** Advanced governance and quality capabilities, including support for Al assisted profiling and mapping, data quality assessment of inputs and resolved entities, as well as enforcing enterprise data quality and privacy policies for master data is provided by an additional subscription of IBM watsonx.data intelligence Standard plan.
